017-10-03T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭講到唔係公仔麵落湯粉<br />\n又有晒材料<br />\n以為有得睇下點熬個辣湯底<br />\n點知原來又係靠辣椒粉同胡椒粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁同烚熟d野擺埋一碗有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另外可以試下present靚d<br />\n留幾粒蔥花最後落<br />\n又或者執起d餸 落少d湯<br />\n而家呢張完全無食慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0a08bdb257f9d6ee65a4193f8bfe4b91bd3890","tid":422801,"uid":95544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一開頭講到唔係公仔麵落湯粉<br />\n又有晒材料<br />\n以為有得睇下點熬個辣湯底<br />\n點知原來又係靠辣椒粉同胡椒粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁同烚熟d野擺埋一碗有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另外可以試下present靚d<br />\n留幾粒蔥花最後落<br />\n又或者執起d餸 落少d湯<br />\n而家呢張完全無食慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係睇一個韓國節目教咁煮嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國好多都落辣椒粉㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b08be3fb2964b5b78bf99be1f124af562f94a5","tid":422801,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"魷魚呀，我好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4bcf1133c9890a2d007aad939a18a60caf80f3","tid":422801,"uid":95544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魷魚呀，我好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次都係買魷魚圈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b664fa2cb24914c28bf28f3ed299b1cfe8a72bdc","tid":422801,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>魷魚呀，我好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"h